parameters: [Principal] Could it be... you're asking for money again today...?
[Anastasia] (There hasn't been any change up until now...)
[Anastasia] (....That woman... What on earth is she....)

[Principal] Anastasia-sama... How on earth did you manage to obtain
such a large sum of money?
[Anastasia] It doesn't matter, right? Such things.

[Anastasia] For now, with this, I'll be staying as usual for today and
tomorrow...

[Principal] (Grumble... This is completely different from what we were
talking about...)
[Principal] (That woman... What on earth is she planning...)

[Principal] Th-That... Anastasia... She somehow managed to gather the
money from somewhere...
[Gizelmina] It's fine, everything is going smoothly
[Gizelmina] If you keep watching, you'll understand eventually
I paid 180,000G for two days' worth.

[Anastasia] Even after one day has passed... there hasn't been any
change...

[Anastasia] Considering that woman... It's hard to believe that she
hasn't done anything...
